name: Koinos
public_notice: A snapshot of the KOIN ERC-20 tokens was taken on October 31st in preparation for the Koinos main net launch on November 5th. If you would like to claim your main net tokens, go here: website

description.en: KOIN will be the cryptocurrency that powers Koinos; a high performance, scalable, general purpose blockchain capable of rapid evolution. It is currently a PoW mineable ERC-20 that will determine the initial token supply of the Koinos mainnet at launch.
